creator: VisitOSLO
descriptionHtml:
With this free Oslo Pass-app you can buy the official city card of Oslo. It offers free entry to more than 30 museums and attractions, free travel on all public transport in the city, discounts on sightseeing and special offers at restaurants and leisure activities.

Key features:

• The Oslo Pass is available for 24, 48 or 72 hours. Reduced rated for children and seniors
• English language
• Map function of Oslo, showing all the offers
• Works both offline or online (updates and sharing must be done online)
• Buy one or multiple Oslo Passes in one purchase, and activate them on the same device
• Buy the Oslo Pass in advance if you want, and activate it when you arrive in Oslo (must be activated within one year after purchase)
• Can be purchased with an international credit card in the app

Combine the Oslo Pass-app with visiting our website visitoslo.com, which is a complete guide to Oslo and includes updated information about top attractions, sightseeing, restaurants, shopping, events, transport, hotels and the day-to-day event listings with concerts, festivals, theatre, tours, sporting events, exhibitions, markets, children’s events and more.

Enjoy Oslo!
oslopass@visitoslo.com
